hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 定义 
$$\alpha_0=\frac{\sqrt{m k_0}}{\hbar},\quad \alpha_1=\frac{\sqrt{m k_1}}{\hbar}=\frac{\sqrt{m\,(4k_0)}}{\hbar}=2\alpha_0.$$
2. 交叠系数为
$$c_0=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\Bigl(\frac{\alpha_1}{\pi}\Bigr)^{1/4}e^{-\frac{\alpha_1x^2}{2}}
\Bigl(\frac{\alpha_0}{\pi}\Bigr)^{1/4}e^{-\frac{\alpha_0x^2}{2}}\,dx
=\frac{(\alpha_0\alpha_1)^{1/4}}{\sqrt{\pi}}
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}e^{-\frac{\alpha_0+\alpha_1}{2}x^2}\,dx.$$
3. 使用 
$$\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}e^{-B x^2}dx=\sqrt{\frac{\pi}{B}},\quad B=\frac{\alpha_0+\alpha_1}{2},$$
因此
$$c_0=\frac{(\alpha_0\alpha_1)^{1/4}}{\sqrt{\pi}}\sqrt{\frac{\pi}{(\alpha_0+\alpha_1)/2}}
=\frac{(\alpha_0\alpha_1)^{1/4}}{\sqrt{(\alpha_0+\alpha_1)/2}}\,. $$
4. 概率为
$$P=|c_0|^2=\frac{2\sqrt{\alpha_0\alpha_1}}{\alpha_0+\alpha_1}
=\frac{2\sqrt{\alpha_0\,(2\alpha_0)}}{\alpha_0+2\alpha_0}
=\frac{2\sqrt{2}\,\alpha_0}{3\alpha_0}
=\frac{2\sqrt{2}}{3}\,. $$
